# SOP Snippet (for NTU – AI and Society)

I developed an AI-powered chatbot to promote waste segregation in a 400+ household community. Using NLP and multiple ML models, I built a retrainable system that adapts to new user data and tracks its performance. The project reflects my commitment to responsible, accessible, and civic-centered AI – values central to NTU’s AI and Society program.
